01:03:25.135 --> 01:03:27.103
[긴장되는 음악]

01:03:27.170 --> 01:03:28.608
(기자) Thank you so much for today

01:03:28.675 --> 01:03:29.992
(소라) Thank you

01:03:32.467 --> 01:03:33.876
God job everyone

01:03:33.943 --> 01:03:35.423
